---
// Scene 3: Theory in Live Action
// Embed a REAL recorded steering episode
// Token-by-token animation with entropy + gate flashes
// CTA to live app to do it themselves
---

<section id="action" class="section-divider">
  <div class="prose-section">
    <h2>Theory in live action: watch a steering episode</h2>

    <p class="text-lg">
      Below is a real steering trace from one of the confirmed runs: baseline generation vs
      gated steering. Watch the tokens come out, the gating events (golden flashes when entropy
      crosses the threshold), and the behavioral lift (the model learns to steer toward a registered concept).
    </p>

    <div class="my-12 p-8 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
      <div id="trace-player" class="w-full h-96 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex-1 bg-black rounded overflow-hidden mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-center">
            <span class="block text-sm mb-2">Interactive trace player</span>
            <span class="text-xs">(Loads trained_bridge_qwen3 steering trace)</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <button id="play-button" class="flex-1 bg-accent text-white py-2 rounded font-semibold text-sm hover:opacity-90">
            ▶ Play
          </button>
          <div class="flex-1 bg-gray-800 rounded h-10 flex items-center px-4">
            <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 h-2 rounded cursor-pointer" id="progress-bar"></div>
          </div>
          <span id="time-display" class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm w-16 text-right">0:00</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
        <div class="p-4 bg-gray-800 rounded">
          <div class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-bright">0.44</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-muted mt-2">Baseline lift (gated)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-gray-800 rounded">
          <div class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-success">✓</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-muted mt-2">Within entropy budget</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-gray-800 rounded">
          <div class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-accent">12–14</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-muted mt-2">Gated write events</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
      <a href="https://prabodha.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-button">
        Try it yourself →
      </a>
      <a href="#comparison" class="secondary-button">
        See all traces
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-sm text-muted mt-8">
      <strong>Trace source:</strong> gate_L20_confirm, seed 42 ·
      <strong>Model:</strong> Qwen3-4B, temperature 0.8 ·
      <strong>Concept:</strong> Registered steering target (from corpus)
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const playButton = document.getElementById('play-button');
  if (playButton) {
    playButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
      alert('In production, this loads a real trace from apps/web/public/data/replays/ and animates it.');
    });
  }
</script>
